Class CUDPPAlgorithm

java.lang.Object
  jcuda.jcudpp.CUDPPAlgorithm

public class CUDPPAlgorithm
extends java.lang.Object

Algorithms supported by CUDPP. Used to create appropriate plans using cudppPlan.

See Also:
CUDPPConfiguration, JCudpp.cudppPlan(jcuda.jcudpp.CUDPPHandle, jcuda.jcudpp.CUDPPConfiguration, long, long, long)
